{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_51_02",
  "title": "miho 2話 小料理屋miho",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "……ん～！　mihoさん、この厚揚げ、とっても\n美味しいです。こんなに美味しいの初めて食べました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mmm~! Miho-san‚ this deep-fried tofu is so good!\nThis is the first time I’ve had something this good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 10.8666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "下見のついでに作っただけよ。さすが、プロが普段から\n使っている厨房ね。いい道具が揃ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was just a test to check things in advance. As expected of a kitchen\nused by professionals‚ they have great tools.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6360463238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.5666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "企画で、こんなお店を使わせてもらえるなんて\nありがたいですよね。あ、おかわりいただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's great that we can use a place like this\nfor our project. Oh‚ can I have some more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 26.7333333969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "ないわよ。ついでに作っただけと言ったでしょう\nそれに、瑠依も作る側……『店員役』をやるんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All gone‚ I told you that was just for the test.\nAnd you’re supposed to be on the cooking side… as the role of “waitress.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 35.4666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。この間お伝えしたように、飲食店のCMに出る\nことがあっても、私自身はアルバイトの経験もないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. As I mentioned before‚ even though I’ve appeared in restaurant commercials‚\nI’ve never actually worked part-time at one‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 45.2000000636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "より、スポンサーさんや演出の意図を理解するためにも\n機会があれば、働く経験がしてみたいと思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In order to better understand the intentions of sponsors and directors‚\nI wanted to experience working‚ if I had the chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.8666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……I-UNITYの時は、こちらにも非があったし\n迷惑を掛けた分、参加は認める",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We were also at fault during I-UNITY‚\nSo I’ll allow you to participate to make up for the trouble we caused.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 60.1333333969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "けど、腕に自信はあるんでしょうね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you’re confident in your skills‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 63.6666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのみなさんのことは、恨んではいません\n決着はステージの上でつけたいと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t resent everyone in IIIX.\nI want to settle things on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 70.8666667302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "その上で……こう見えて私、料理にかける想いは\n人一倍強いんです。純粋に、挑戦させてほしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On top of that… Despite how I look‚ I have a strong passion for cooking\nmore than others. I sincerely want to give this a try.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.5333333969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "威勢がいいわね。分かったわ、『小料理屋miho』の\n看板を背負う覚悟があるなら、厨房に立ちなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re full of spirit. Alright‚ if you have the guts\nto carry the name of “Izakaya miho‚” then get in the kitchen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 87.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 89.8333313624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、凄い気迫……。だけど……気合いが入り\n過ぎて、なんだか変なことになってるような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They both have such intense energy…. But… They’re so fired up\nThat things seem to be going in a strange direction……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8800562541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 101.599998029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "というか、瑠依って料理、上手だったかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ was Rui good at cooking…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.599998029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 107.1333313624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "では、早速始めます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ let’s begin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1333313624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 110.6666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ご飯が炊けた……水分量も時間も完璧……\nここに……混ぜる……！　はぁぁぁ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The rice is done… The water ratio and cooking time were perfect…\nNow to… mix it in…! Haaaaah!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 119.0666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 120.5666580836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "凄い……！\n瑠依、予想以上だわ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing…!\nRui‚ you’re better than I expected…！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 125.5999914169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "出来ました。これが私の――\nゴボウとタケノコの混ぜご飯……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here it is. My――\nBurdock and bamboo shoot mixed rice……!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 131.8999903996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "――を、グミでアレンジしたものです！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――arranged with gummy candy!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8999903996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 135.6666570663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "予想以上に料理が下手っ！\nというかもう下手とかいう次元じゃない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re worse at cooking than I expected!\nThis is beyond bad……!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 142.1666570663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依、一ついいかしら\nなぜ、ほかほかのご飯にグミを混ぜているの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui‚ can I ask you something?\nWhy did you mix gummy candy into hot rice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 149.433323733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "なぜって……その方が美味しくなるからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… It tastes better that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.433323733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_51_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "この前、沙季が作った混ぜご飯が美味しかったから\n具材をグミに変えたら、もっと美味しくなると思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki made some mixed rice the other day that was good‚\nSo I thought it would be even better if I replaced the ingredients with gummy candy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.2666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 161.2999903996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
